The basic thing is that you must update the JProgressBar from the Swing Thread will doing your long-running process in the background thread, such as that provided by a SwingWorker object. There are too many details for us to review all here, and so all I can do is provide a link, but we&#39;ll be happy to help you understand the details once you review the tutorials. Just check the tutorials and come on back with your specific questions if you&#39;re still stuck.

**Edit 1**  
You state:  
